        "text-0": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Haze was born from a frustration most of us share \u2014 a bathroom drawer full of tools that don\u2019t work well and don\u2019t look beautiful together. We wanted a single kit that felt intentional: tools that are gentle, materials that last, and a ritual worth doing every morning.<\/p>",
